    *    **Middle Layer**: The yellow rectangular block lies flat bridging the two orange cylinders. The blue cube sits on the flat yellow block. The red arch sits on the yellow block with the blue one sitting beside it.
    *    **Top Layer**: The orange cylinder sits straight on the previous layer. The orange triangle block sits on the very top of the cylinder.
